<abstract abstract-type="short" xml:lang="en"><p><![CDATA[In this interview, Pedro Pontual, psychologist and Doctor of Education at Pontifícia Universidade Católica de São Paulo (PUC-SP), exposes the history of the National Policy of Social Participation (PNPS) development and talks at length about the circumstances and the difficulties involved in the implementation of a participation system.]]></p></abstract>
